<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>寂静·流年</title><link>https://example.com/</link><description>记录我的生活、兴趣和研究</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><copyright>This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Jan 2022 14:37:25 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://example.com/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>如何使用windows的资源管理器打开FTP</title><link>https://example.com/posts/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8windows%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80ftp/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jan 2022 14:37:25 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>https://example.com/posts/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8windows%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80ftp/</guid><description>我是习惯用专用的FTP软件来连接FTP,比如FlashFXP等, 但是也有人喜欢用windows资源管理器连接FTP服务器，且不用老输入用户名</description></item><item><title>Linux主目录下的文件名改成英文</title><link>https://example.com/posts/linux%E4%B8%BB%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8D%E6%94%B9%E6%88%90%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jan 2022 07:24:41 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>https://example.com/posts/linux%E4%B8%BB%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8D%E6%94%B9%E6%88%90%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87/</guid><description>之所以要改成英文名称,是为了在终端下操作方便。 一、打开终端，在终端中输入命令: 1 2 export LANG=en_US xdg-user-dirs-gtk-update 跳出对话框询问是否将目录转化为英文路径,同意并关闭。</description></item><item><title>使用Hugo搭建个人网站(四)-使用Github Action自动部署到Github Pages</title><link>https://example.com/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E5%9B%9B-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8github-action%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0github-pages/</link><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jan 2022 11:10:10 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>https://example.com/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E5%9B%9B-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8github-action%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0github-pages/</guid><description>部署网站到Github上使用的是Github Page功能。 一般来说，部署Hugo网站到Github Page的流程是这样的： 新建一个Githu</description></item><item><title>使用Hugo搭建个人网站(三)-LoveIt主题启用网站图标</title><link>https://example.com/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E4%B8%89-loveit%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jan 2022 18:07:38 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>https://example.com/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E4%B8%89-loveit%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87/</guid><description>网站图标，即favicon,虽然对于网站不是必须的，但是有这个东西能显著增加网站的正规性和美观性。 生成favicon 打开realfavico</description></item><item><title>使用Hugo搭建个人网站(二)-LoveIt主题自定义搜索</title><link>https://example.com/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E4%BA%8C-loveit%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jan 2022 10:51:44 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>https://example.com/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E4%BA%8C-loveit%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2/</guid><description>LoveIt主题自带的搜索插件是lunr和algolia，这两个都不太好用。 在此，我们使用Hugo专用的搜索插件hugo-search-fu</description></item><item><title>使用Hugo搭建个人网站(一)-基本设置和LoveIt主题</title><link>https://example.com/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E4%B8%80-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%92%8Cloveit%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jan 2022 17:27:10 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>https://example.com/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E4%B8%80-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%92%8Cloveit%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>本文使用的软件的版本如下： hugo: 0.91.2-extended loveit主题: 0.2.10 特别注意:hugo必须使用extended版本 关于Hugo的安装和网站的生成，本文不再详述</description></item></channel></rss>